reviews.review_text: Another Stellar Spring 88 Show Killer recording from CM of a fantastic show. High off the energy from Hampton, the crew nails this show in the big Apple. Scarlet Fire may even be slightly better than Hampton only because the band is getting warmed up.

Charles Miller the Master! Great show show heard first set of 4 1 1988 in Today in Grateful Dead History  with Dave Lemuiex  and than I come here and get my Charles miller soundboard.   Boys are on fire on  this run at  the Meadowlands, in NJ.  Thanks Charles!    Wish I could have gone to some mid to late 80s show still in High school and didn't start following the Dead until 1990.
